---
layout: base.njk
title: Pricing | Hunt Logic AI Plans & Features
description: Choose the Hunt Logic AI plan that fits your hunting style. Free trial available. Premium features start at $29.99/month.
---

{% block content %}

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content text-center" style="max-width: none;">
      <h1>Choose Your Plan</h1>
      <p class="text-large">Start free, upgrade when you're ready. All plans include AI-powered predictions.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <!-- Free Tier -->
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3>Free</h3>
        <div class="pricing-price">$0<span>/month</span></div>
        <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Perfect for trying Hunt Logic AI</p>
        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li>5 trail camera uploads/month</li>
          <li>Basic weather forecasts</li>
          <li>GPS tracking & waypoints</li>
          <li>Community access</li>
          <li>Mobile & web app access</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 2rem;">Start Free</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Premium Tier (Featured) -->
      <div class="pricing-card featured">
        <div style="background: var(--hunter-accent); color: var(--white); text-align: center; padding: 0.5rem; margin: -2rem -2rem 1.5rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg) var(--radius-lg) 0 0; font-weight: 600;">MOST POPULAR</div>
        <h3>Premium</h3>
        <div class="pricing-price">$29.99<span>/month</span></div>
        <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">For serious hunters</p>
        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li>Unlimited trail camera analysis</li>
          <li>AI-powered predictions</li>
          <li>Advanced weather patterns</li>
          <li>Game movement forecasting</li>
          <li>Buck identification & tracking</li>
          <li>Success rate analytics</li>
          <li>Smart hunting alerts</li>
          <li>Priority support</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 2rem;">Start 7-Day Trial</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Pro Tier -->
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3>Pro</h3>
        <div class="pricing-price">$59.99<span>/month</span></div>
        <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">For guides & power users</p>
        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li>Everything in Premium</li>
          <li>Group management (up to 10 users)</li>
          <li>White-label reports</li>
          <li>API access</li>
          <li>Custom integrations</li>
          <li>Dedicated account manager</li>
          <li>Advanced analytics & exports</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 2rem;">Contact Sales</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-3">
      <p style="color: var(--medium-gray);">All plans include iOS, Android, and web access. Cancel anytime. No contracts.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-light">
  <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-3">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <div style="background: var(--white); padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Can I cancel anytime?</h3>
      <p>Yes. Cancel your subscription anytime from your account settings. No contracts, no cancellation fees.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="background: var(--white); padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem;">What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
      <p>We accept all major credit cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover) and PayPal. Subscriptions are billed monthly or annually.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="background: var(--white); padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Is there a free trial?</h3>
      <p>The Free plan is available forever with limited features. Premium and Pro plans include a 7-day free trial - no credit card required to start.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="background: var(--white); padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg);">
      <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Can I upgrade or downgrade later?</h3>
      <p>Absolutely. Change your plan anytime. Upgrades take effect immediately, downgrades take effect at the end of your current billing cycle.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Start Hunting Smarter Today</h2>
    <p>Join 50,000+ hunters using AI to increase their success. Try Premium free for 7 days.</p>
    <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Start Free Trial</a>
  </div>
</section>

{% endblock %}
